{"id": "1515182535976681592", "channel_id": "1510698831434616934", "author_id": "1443227673076699287", "author_name": "mayoineko_73053", "content": "調べていただいてばかりでは申し訳ないので、自分でも攻撃力の合計が異なるように組んで初期値をリストアップしてみました", "timestamp": "2026-06-13T02:34:27.307000+00:00", "thread_id": "1510698831434616934", "attachments": [{"id": "1515182535741538374", "filename": "b8cbed5f3664d0f8.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 30956, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1510698831434616934/1515182535741538374/b8cbed5f3664d0f8.png?ex=6a3401f3&is=6a32b073&hm=97c5acd3bc5fcf19cabe5c79d9a8f7f54cac3d6f93c692673704a9c3e91e7417&"}]}
{"id": "1515182740927025276", "channel_id": "1510698831434616934", "author_id": "1443227673076699287", "author_name": "mayoineko_73053", "content": "傾向として攻撃力の合計が4の倍数から+1したときに切り替わるので、\nまず平均値をとる際に一度切り上げている可能性が高そうです", "timestamp": "2026-06-13T02:35:16.171000+00:00", "thread_id": "1510698831434616934", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-13T02:42:24.179000+00:00"}
